ibe Coding To $1M | Building Prompt Engineering Into BridgeSpace":[54,63],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#De: Day 148 - Vibe Coding To $1M | Building Prompt Engineering Into BridgeSpace#{1}":[56,63],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:":[64,72],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:#{1}":[65,65],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:#{2}":[66,66],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:#{3}":[67,67],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:#{4}":[68,69],"#SAE: context engineering#Solução#Fontes:#{5}":[70,72]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Agentes","target":"#agentes","line":20},{"title":"📚 vibe cod...\n\n有用内容: Gap detectado e resolvido pelo SAE Auto-Evolution Encontradas 5 referências no Obsidian. Verificar notas relacionadas. 有用内容: > **Data:** 2026-03-16 Índice completo de todos os recursos disponíveis no ...\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │                        ARQUITETURA COMPLETA                                  │ ├─────\n\n---\n\n### De: 📚 software architecture DDD event-driven microservices\n\n有用内容：\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │                        ARQUITETURA COMPLETA                                  │ ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │                                                                              │ │  ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐   │ │  │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │    │   Bounded   │   │ │  │   Context   │    │   Context   │    │   Context   │    │   Context   │   │ │  │  (Pedidos)  │    │  (Clientes) │    │  (Estoque)  │    │  (Pagamento)│   │ │  └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘    └──────┬──────┘   │ │         │                  │                  │                  │          \n\n---\n\n### De: Claude AI - 1M Context GA (14/03/2026)\n\n有用内容：\n\n- **Opus 4.6:** $5/input, $25/output por milhão de tokens - **Sonnet 4.6:** $3/input, $15/output por milhão de tokens - Sem multiplicador: 900K tokens = mesma taxa que 9K tokens\n\n- ✅ Rate limits completos em qualquer tamanho de contexto - ✅ **600 imagens ou páginas PDF** por请求 (antes: 100)\n\n- **Contratos longos** - 100+ páginas em uma sessão - **Agentes de IA** - manter trace completo de tool calls e reasoning - **Pesquisa científica** - reasoning across hundreds of papers - **Spreadsheets complexos** - multi-step plans maintained\n\n> \"With 1M context, I search, re-search, aggregate edge cases, and propose fixes — all in one window.\" — Anton Biryukov, Software Engineer\n\n> \"Larger diffs didn't fit in 200K so the agent had to chunk context... With 1M, we get higher-quality reviews.\" — Adhyyan\n\n---\n\n### De: Day 148 - Vibe Coding To $1M | Building Prompt Engineering Into BridgeSpace\n\n有用内容：\n\nThe grind starts early today. We are locked into the flow state for Day 148, and we are fundamentally changing how we interact with our agent swarms. Today, we are building out a massive new prototype for automated prompt engineering. By natively integrating BridgeVoice directly into BridgeSpace, we are going to intercept your raw voice prompt, significantly enhance and engineer it for maximum agentic understanding, and then seamlessly pass it off to Claude Code, Codex, or Gemini CLI. This is how we achieve true coding at the exact speed of thought.\n\n🎙️ BridgeVoice Integration — Wiring our near-immediate voice-to-text engine directly into the BridgeSpace agent development environment for hands-free prompt delivery.\n\n⚡ Automated Prompt Engineering — Building a middleware layer that intercep\n\n### Fontes:\n- [[40-Knowledge/Solutions/sae-multi-chat-context-manager-2026-03-30.md|SAE: multi chat context manager","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN - k_0004 - vibe-coding-practices.md","line":22},{"title":"📚 software architecture DDD event-driven microservices","target":"03-Knowledge/ARES/Knowledge/KN